text: Ljunghusen is a locality in Vellinge Municipality in Skåne County in Sweden. In 2010, 2,555 people lived there. It is located west of Höllviken and east of Skanör-Falsterbo. The place is notable for its beaches and for its golf course. == References == ==Other websites== Category:Settlements in Skane County
